title.text: K9 & Company: A Girl's Best Friend

item.description: A compelling and witty drama starring Stellan Skarsg\xe5rd as John River, a brilliant detective whose fractured mind traps him between the living and the dead.
Gripping crime drama starring Gillian Anderson as DSI Stella Gibson, the detective investigating a serial killer that stalks his victims whilst hiding in plain sight.
Carla gets propositioned while trying to help Peter. Aaron gives Summer the brush-off. Sarah tasks Kirk with another tricky sales assignment.
